>>> Router settings <<<

WAN DNS Setting (for Google DNS)
Connect to DNS server automatically -> No
DNS Server1 -> 8.8.8.8
DNS Server2 -> 8.8.4.4

LAN -> DHCP server
DNS and WINS Server Setting
DNS Server1 -> 192.168.29.244 (RPi ip adress)
Advertise router's IP -> No
Forward local domian -> No

Make sure that RPi has static IP selected

>>> Pi-hole settings <<<
 
 Settings -> DNS
 + Use Conditional Forwarding
 IP of router + local doamin name
